headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Intuitive Surgical After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Intuitive Surgical is still worth buying at these levels, or if the easy gains are already behind it, you are not alone. That is exactly what we are going to unpack. The stock has inched up about 0.2% over the last week, 1.8% over the last month, and 6.8% year to date. Its longer term 3 year and 5 year gains of 113.7% and 105.9% show how powerful the story has been, even if the 2.6% 1 year return looks more muted.
